description:
- Soft White Coat "A soft and fluffy coat in the shape of a white rabbit. "
 - Soft Kid's White Rabbit "A soft and fluffy white-rabbit suit for children. "
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop( Clothing Store in Castle St. ) when you purchase it. 
 - White Rabbit Baby Suit "A white-rabbit costume for babies. "
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop( Fashion Store in Castle St. ) when you purchase it.
name: Fluffy White-Rabbit Set
